            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="/s3/files/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-04/20220425_news_taiwan.jpg?itok=hmhxA3L_" title="台湾疫情持续恶化，4月25日新增5108起本土确诊病例。（彭博社）" alt="台湾疫情持续恶化，4月25日新增5108起本土确诊病例。（彭博社）" src="https://www.zaobao.com/s3/files/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-04/20220425_news_taiwan.jpg?itok=hmhxA3L_" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
